# Hybrid model (CLAUDE.md Constraints): the skeleton is tracked, payload is not.
# Structure is versioned; content binaries in the areas are ignored.

# payload binaries anywhere in the areas
*.pptx
*.ppt
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.docx
*.doc
*.pdf
*.zip
*.7z
*.msg
*.eml
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.vsdx

# but fixtures and skills are skeleton — always tracked
!tests/**
!skills/**

# generated output — regenerate via skills/orbit-dashboard/generate.py
dashboard.html

# OS noise
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
__pycache__/
